<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٦٤ - <span class="c2">(٢٦٣٩)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">ابْنُ الْمُثَنَّى</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">وَابْنُ بَشَّارٍ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ جَعْفَرٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ </a>سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا</a> <span class="c2">(ح)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>